Q: MySQL UNCOMPRESS() returns NULL in 8.0.37 but works in 5.7 A: <p>This answer is speculative, but it rests on the observation that the apparent length of <code>my_column</code> is 2543 on your MySQL 5.7 database, but only 1140 on MySQL 8.</p>
<p>I suggest that you check the <em>encodings</em> on both databases, tables, and columns.</p>
<pre class="lang-sql prettyprint-override"><code>SHOW CREATE TABLE my_table;
SHOW FULL COLUMNS FROM my_table;
</code></pre>
<p>Run the above 2 commands on both your MySQL 5.7 and 8.0 databases and see if you can find a difference in collation.</p>

Q: Combine onMomentumScrollBegin and abortController in react native to avoid duplicate page fetches A: <p>Full Flatlist code using basic functionality offered by <em>phuocantd</em>'s answer:</p>
<pre><code>import React, { useCallback, useEffect, useRef, useState } from 'react';
import {
  ActivityIndicator,
  FlatList,
  ListRenderItemInfo,
  StyleSheet,
  Text,
  View,
} from 'react-native';

const API_URL = 'https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts';
const PAGE_SIZE = 20;

type Item = {
  id: number;
  title: string;
  body: string;
};

async function fetchPage(page: number, signal?: AbortSignal): Promise&lt;Item[]&gt; {
  console.log('Fetching page:', `${API_URL}?_limit=${PAGE_SIZE}&amp;_page=${page}`, { signal });
  const res = await fetch(`${API_URL}?_limit=${PAGE_SIZE}&amp;_page=${page}`);
  if (!res.ok) throw new Error('Failed to fetch data');
  return res.json();
}

const ListItem = React.memo(({ item }: { item: Item }) =&gt; (
  &lt;View style={styles.item}&gt;
    &lt;Text style={styles.title}&gt;{item.title}&lt;/Text&gt;
    &lt;Text style={styles.desc}&gt;{item.body}&lt;/Text&gt;
  &lt;/View&gt;
));

const InfiniteList: React.FC = () =&gt; {
  const [data, setData] = useState&lt;Item[]&gt;([]);
  const [page, setPage] = useState(1);
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);
  const [hasMore, setHasMore] = useState(true);

  const abortRef = useRef&lt;AbortController | null&gt;(null);
  const onEndReachedCalledDuringMomentum = useRef(false);

  // Initial load only once
  useEffect(() =&gt; {
    loadMore();
    // eslint-disable-next-line react-hooks/exhaustive-deps
  }, []);

  const loadMore = useCallback(async () =&gt; {
    if (loading || !hasMore) return;

    setLoading(true);
    abortRef.current?.abort();
    const controller = new AbortController();
    abortRef.current = controller;

    try {
      const items = await fetchPage(page, controller.signal);
      setData((prev) =&gt; [...prev, ...items]);
      setHasMore(items.length === PAGE_SIZE);
      setPage((prev) =&gt; prev + 1);
    } catch (err: any) {
      if (err.name !== 'AbortError') console.warn('Fetch error:', err);
    } finally {
      setLoading(false);
    }
  }, [loading, hasMore, page]);

  const handleEndReached = useCallback(() =&gt; {
    if (!onEndReachedCalledDuringMomentum.current &amp;&amp; !loading &amp;&amp; hasMore) {
      loadMore();
      onEndReachedCalledDuringMomentum.current = true;
    }
  }, [loading, hasMore, loadMore]);

  const keyExtractor = useCallback((item: Item) =&gt; item.id.toString(), []);
  const renderItem = useCallback(
    ({ item }: ListRenderItemInfo&lt;Item&gt;) =&gt; &lt;ListItem item={item} /&gt;,
    []
  );

  const ListFooter = useCallback(
    () =&gt;
      loading ? (
        &lt;View style={styles.footer}&gt;
          &lt;ActivityIndicator color=&quot;#666&quot; size=&quot;small&quot; /&gt;
        &lt;/View&gt;
      ) : null,
    [loading]
  );

  return (
    &lt;FlatList
      data={data}
      keyExtractor={keyExtractor}
      renderItem={renderItem}
      onEndReached={handleEndReached}
      onEndReachedThreshold={0.7}
      onMomentumScrollBegin={() =&gt; {
        onEndReachedCalledDuringMomentum.current = false;
      }}
      ListFooterComponent={ListFooter}
      contentContainerStyle={styles.container}
      showsVerticalScrollIndicator={false}
      removeClippedSubviews
      initialNumToRender={10}
      maxToRenderPerBatch={10}
      windowSize={10}
    /&gt;
  );
};

export default InfiniteList;

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    paddingBottom: 20,
  },
  item: {
    backgroundColor: '#fff',
    marginHorizontal: 16,
    marginVertical: 8,
    borderRadius: 8,
    elevation: 2,
    padding: 12,
  },
  title: {
    fontSize: 16,
    fontWeight: '600',
    color: '#111',
    marginBottom: 6,
  },
  desc: {
    fontSize: 14,
    color: '#444',
  },
  footer: {
    paddingVertical: 16,
  },
});
</code></pre>

